<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-5588] Add get commands to nodetool for things with set</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5588</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Can we add:&lt;br/&gt;
nodetool getcompactionthroughput&lt;br/&gt;
nodetool getstreamthroughput&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To go with the set commands?  You currently have to fire up a JMX client to know what the current values are.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
